      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a great little project to tinker with. Easy on the wallet and priced to move, it\u2019s a straightforward car from a seller who believes in being upfront and easy to deal with. If you want something cheap, usable, and full of potential, this one is worth a look.",
